Package com.dumbdogdiner.stickyapi.common.nbt

This package contains classes designed to help work with SNBT
Since:
3.0
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    NbtTag  
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    NbtBooleanTag
    A convenience class for converting booleans from JsonPrimitives, and for easily creating
    NbtCompoundTag
    A wrapper tag that allows working with Compound NBT tags as maps!
    NbtJsonAdapter
    Utility class for easy creation of the appropriate NbtTag from an existing JsonElement
    NbtJsonTag
    A special type of NbtTag that converts an arbitrary JsonElement into an appropriately escaped string as NBT
    NbtListTag
    A wrapper class that allows the construction of or conversion (from JSON) of NBT List Tags
    NbtNumberTag
    A wrapper class that allows you to deal with numbers in NBT
    NbtPrimitiveTag<T>
    Base class for any NBT tags that wrap simple primitives (and strings)
    NbtStringTag
    A NbtTag that wraps and escapes Strings
